[center][size=4]Tushani is one of my player presets. This preset was used to make the Follower Tushani by sleepytigereyes.

To make Tushani appear as in the images you will need the following mods.

Race: Imperial
True eyes : Human Black Ebony
KS Hairdos : 0Bella

Image 1 and 2
Fair Skin Complexion

Image 3
Demoniac  Skin Texture 

The brows are vanilla skyrim Human 09

[/size][size=5]Installation:
[/size][size=4]Drop the .jslot file into your SKSE/pluggins/Chargen/Presets folder[/size][size=4]
